text.title: Brown Rabbit
text.tspan: Well, that was tasty. Hey, I
have to hurry out now, but
here's my share of the bill.

text.title: Lucy Usagi
text.tspan: Wait wait wait, that's too much.

text.title: Brown Rabbit
text.tspan: Oh, don't worry about it. I really--

text.title: Tort Bunny
text.tspan: I cut you! I cut you now!
Cite as: Andrew Fong, Inconsiderate, TORT BUNNIES (April 4, 2011), http://tortbunnies.com/89.html.
